head.note:
In English and French;
                                    French text not printed. Ratification advised by the Senate,
                                    Mar. 30, 1922; ratified by the President, June 9, 1923;
                                    instruments of ratification deposited at Washington, Aug. 5,
                                    1925; proclaimed, Aug. 5, 1925.

